<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7380> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7380" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Pr. procos., uncertain date. Named in an inscription of Teanum Sidicinum, of late republican or early Augustan date (Eph. Epig. 8.217, no. 883; PIR P 10). Syme notes also ...cius Balbus (see MRR 2.483), a legatus named also in an inscription of Cos (Aepig. 1934, no. 85). Perhaps the same man; there is space for about eight letters. (RS, MS-RP 1.285)\n" .
